1. Run app, open netlist, verify Goals dialog appears before model selection.
2. Set Area priority=10, Matching=0, Symmetry=0 → confirm LLM prompt contains "Minimise rows" instruction and composite weights area heavily.
3. Set Symmetry=10 → confirm symmetry enforcer runs and composite weights symmetry metrics.
4. Set max_area=5µm² on a design that produces 8µm² → confirm warning is displayed.
